text:
──At first, I was a little worried, but
it turned out well, didn't it?
I was able to build a good relationship with the staff too.

Mikoto, as you were leaving,
the staff seemed really grateful to you.

Yeah,
they said they want you to come back again.

It's great that your true charm,
seems to have come across.

Producer, it seems like
you understand me well.
